title: Duke Falls to Virginia Tech, 6-1 - Duke University - GoDuke.com
content: Duke Falls to Virginia Tech, 6-1 - Duke University  GoDuke.com
description: Rookie southpaw Jonathan Santucci put together a strong outing, but it wasn't enough as the Duke baseball team dropped a 6-1 decision to Virginia Tech on Friday night at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
